• Review and investigate the remaining CIP accounts and transfer all completed PPAs to proper PPE accounts in consideration with the certificate of completion, inspection report and other necessary documents from the City Engineering Office;
• Provide depreciation to those transferred PPEs for proper presentation in the Financial Statements;
